- to enter mongo shell
mongo

- to connect to db or create new db
use dbname

- to show all dbs in the server

show dbs

- to show what is the db currently connected

db

- to insert in to db

db.movie.insert({"name":"Lucifer"})

- to drop database 

db.dropDatabase()  

- to query documents

db.COLLECTION_NAME.find({})   
db.movie.find()
db.movie.find({})

